query.pigql: totalAttach = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceKnowledgeAttached_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; totalAttach = filter totalAttach by {{column(Vote_Stat_Normalized_Chart.selection, ["ArticleVersion_Title"]).asEquality("Article_ArticleVersion_Title")}};totalAttach = filter totalAttach by {{column(View_Count_Normalized_Chart.selection, ["ArticleVersion_Title"]).asEquality("Article_ArticleVersion_Title")}};totalAttach = filter totalAttach by {{column(select_InternalChannel.selection, ["ArticleVersion_IsVisibleInApp"]).asEquality("Article_ArticleVersion_IsVisibleInApp")}};totalAttach = filter totalAttach by {{column(select_PartnerChannel.selection, ["ArticleVersion_IsVisibleInPrm"]).asEquality("Article_ArticleVersion_IsVisibleInPrm")}};totalAttach = filter totalAttach by {{column(select_CustomerChannel.selection, ["ArticleVersion_IsVisibleInCsp"]).asEquality("Article_ArticleVersion_IsVisibleInCsp")}};totalAttach = filter totalAttach by {{column(select_PublicChannel.selection, ["ArticleVersion_IsVisibleInPkb"]).asEquality("Article_ArticleVersion_IsVisibleInPkb")}}; totalAttach = filter totalAttach by {{column(Publish_Article_Select.selection, ["ArticleVersion_PublishStatus"]).asEquality("Article_ArticleVersion_PublishStatus")}};citation = filter totalAttach by isAttachedByOwner == "false"; citationAttach = group totalAttach by all,citation by all ; citationPercent = foreach citationAttach generate count(citation)/count(totalAttach) as unique_percent;

rank() over([..] partition by all order by B desc)

Knowledge_Article_Table.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceKnowledge_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; r = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceKnowledgeAttached_tp.FullyQualifiedName}";q = filter q by {{column(View_Count_Normalized_Chart.selection, ["ArticleVersion_Title"]).asEquality("ArticleVersion_Title")}}; q = filter q by {{column(Vote_Stat_Normalized_Chart.selection, ["ArticleVersion_Title"]).asEquality("ArticleVersion_Title")}};  r = filter r by {{column(Article_Attached_Count_Chart.result, ["Article_ArticleVersion_Title"]).asEquality("Article_ArticleVersion_Title")}}; r = filter r by {{column(Article_Attached_Count_Chart.selection, ["Article_ArticleVersion_Title"]).asEquality("Article_ArticleVersion_Title")}}; s = cogroup q by ('Id','ArticleVersion_Title') full, r by ('KnowledgeArticleId','Article_ArticleVersion_Title'); s = foreach s generate (case when ("{{cell(Case_Reason_Select.selection, 0, "Case_Reason").asObject()}}"!= ""  ||  "{{cell(Case_Product_Select.selection, 0, "Case_Product_Family_KB__c").asObject()}}"!= "" ||  "{{cell(Article_Attached_Count_Chart.selection, 0, "Article_ArticleVersion_Title").asObject()}}"!= "") then r['Article_ArticleVersion_Title'] else q['ArticleVersion_Title'] end) as 'Article Title', q['Id'] as 'Id', first(q['User_Name']) as 'Article Creator',first(q['ArticleVersion_PublishStatus']) as 'Publish Status',first(q['ArticleVersion_VersionNumber']) as 'Version Number',first(q['ChannelList']) as 'Channel List',first(q['CreatedDate']) as 'Created Date',first(q['LastPublishedDate']) as 'Last Published Date', count(q) as 'count'; s = filter s by 'Article Title' is not null;

query.pigql: totalArticles = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceKnowledge_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; attachedArticles = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceKnowledgeAttached_tp.FullyQualifiedName}";totalArticles = filter totalArticles by {{column(View_Count_Normalized_Chart.selection, ["ArticleVersion_Title"]).asEquality("ArticleVersion_Title")}}; totalArticles = filter totalArticles by {{column(Vote_Stat_Normalized_Chart.selection, ["ArticleVersion_Title"]).asEquality("ArticleVersion_Title")}};  attachedArticles = filter attachedArticles by {{column(Article_Attached_Count_Chart.result, ["Article_ArticleVersion_Title"]).asEquality("Article_ArticleVersion_Title")}}; attachedArticles = filter attachedArticles by {{column(Article_Attached_Count_Chart.selection, ["Article_ArticleVersion_Title"]).asEquality("Article_ArticleVersion_Title")}}; combined = cogroup totalArticles by 'ArticleVersion_Title' full, attachedArticles by 'Article_ArticleVersion_Title'; combined = foreach combined generate (case when ("{{cell(Case_Reason_Select.selection, 0, "Case_Reason").asObject()}}"!= "all"  ||  "{{cell(Case_Product_Select.selection, 0, "Case_Product_Family_KB__c").asObject()}}"!= "all" ||  "{{cell(Article_Attached_Count_Chart.selection, 0, "Article_ArticleVersion_Title").asObject()}}"!= "all") then attachedArticles['Article_ArticleVersion_Title'] else totalArticles['ArticleVersion_Title'] end) as 'ArticleVersion_Title',sum(totalArticles['VoteStat_NormalizedScore']) as 'sum_VoteStat_NormalizedScore'; combined = filter combined by not('ArticleVersion_Title' is null); combined = order combined by 'sum_VoteStat_NormalizedScore' desc;

totalArticles = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceKnowledge_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; attachedArticles = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceKnowledgeAttached_tp.FullyQualifiedName}";totalArticles = filter totalArticles by {{column(View_Count_Normalized_Chart.selection, ["ArticleVersion_Title"]).asEquality("ArticleVersion_Title")}}; totalArticles = filter totalArticles by {{column(Vote_Stat_Normalized_Chart.selection, ["ArticleVersion_Title"]).asEquality("ArticleVersion_Title")}}; attachedArticles = filter attachedArticles by {{column(Article_Attached_Count_Chart.result, ["Article_ArticleVersion_Title"]).asEquality("Article_ArticleVersion_Title")}}; attachedArticles = filter attachedArticles by {{column(Article_Attached_Count_Chart.selection, ["Article_ArticleVersion_Title"]).asEquality("Article_ArticleVersion_Title")}}; combined = cogroup totalArticles by 'ArticleVersion_Title' full, attachedArticles by 'Article_ArticleVersion_Title'; combined = foreach combined generate (case when ("{{cell(Case_Reason_Select.selection, 0, "Case_Reason").asObject()}}"!= "all"  ||  "{{cell(Case_Product_Select.selection, 0, "Case_Product_Family_KB__c").asObject()}}"!= "all" ||  "{{cell(Article_Attached_Count_Chart.selection, 0, "Article_ArticleVersion_Title").asObject()}}"!= "all") then attachedArticles['Article_ArticleVersion_Title'] else totalArticles['ArticleVersion_Title'] end) as 'ArticleVersion_Title', sum(totalArticles['ViewStat_ViewCount']) as 'sum_ViewStat_ViewCount'; combined = filter combined by not('ArticleVersion_Title' is null); combined = order combined by 'sum_ViewStat_ViewCount' desc;
